  "description": "A Curios/Trinket like plugin for PaperMC",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\" style=\"line-height:0;\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/relique/banner.png\" />\n  <br/>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/e35gP423vN\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/general_parts/discord_dark.png\"/></a><a href=\"https://jitpack.io/#darksoulq/Relique\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage@main/plugin_icons/v1/general_parts/builds_dark.png\"/></a><a href=\"https://darksoulq.github.io/Relique/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/general_parts/docs_dark.png\"/></a>\n</div>\n\n---\n## Requirements:\nThe plugin requires [AbyssalLib](https://modrinth.com/plugin/abyssallib)\n\n## Features\n\nA Curios-like Plugin for PaperMC servers\n\n- JSON based Slots\n- Slot attributes supporting modifiers to increase limits\n- All entities can have relics (defined in JSON)\n- 5 Default slots (head, chest, ring, belt, charm)\n- Builtin Attribute modifier and equip/unequip sound support\n- API for custom slot validators and much more.\n\nAnd much more.\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\">\n  <a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/relique/inventory.png\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/relique/inventory.png\" width=\"100%\" />\n  </a><br/>\n  <sub><b>The Inventory</b></sub>\n</td>\n<td align=\"center\" width=\"50%\">\n  <a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/relique/totem.gif\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/darksoulq/ImageStorage/plugin_icons/v1/relique/totem.gif\" width=\"100%\" />\n  </a><br/>\n  <sub><b>Totem in Charm slot (Not bundled!)</b></sub>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n</div>\n\n## Credits\n\n- [Curios](https://modrinth.com/mod/curios)",
